properties.headline: FLOODING MOREE TO BOGGABILLA Newell Highway
properties.diversions:
Northbound motorists from Moree can use the Canarvon Hwy and then join the Barwon Hwy to Goondiwindi.

Southbound motorists from Boggabilla can use the Barwon Hwy from Goondiwindi and then join the Canarvon Hwy to Moree.

This route is suitable for all vehicles.

properties.headline: FLOODING MACQUARIE PASS Illawarra Highway
properties.otherAdvice: Illawarra Highway is also closed between Tongarra Road and M1 Princes Motorway
properties.diversions:
Light vehicles: via Jamberoo Mountain Rd and should allow an extra 10 minutes travel time between Robertson and Albion Park.

Heavy vehicles: via the Hume Hwy, Picton Rd and the M1 Princes Mwy and should allow an additional 30 minutes travel time between the Hume Mwy and Albion Park.
